{"tid":1838804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓確診第二宗肺炎 Red Velvet成員Irene疑受感染","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T06:50:10.000Z","uid":288229,"like":39,"dislike":168,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b30f43f1fe669dda1fb0eb4ed0b5c03e03062dd5","tid":1838804,"uid":288229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7zJCt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7zJCt7.jpg&h=95c94048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（中央社記者姜遠珍首爾24日專電）韓國疾病管理本部今天表示，在韓國境內又發現第2名新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診病例，病患是在中國武漢上班的55歲韓國籍男性，<span style=\"color: red;\">22日經首爾金浦機場入境韓國。</span><br />\n<br />\n南韓聯合新聞通訊社指出，韓國疾病管理本部表示，這名在武漢上班的韓國男性10日因感冒在武漢一家醫院接受治療。<span style=\"color: red;\">這名男性從武漢借道上海於22日晚間搭機返國，在首爾金浦機場入境時，於檢疫站被檢驗出發燒和喉嚨疼痛等症狀。</span><br />\n<br />\n這名男性患者在保健所（社區診所）接受診療後，<span style=\"color: red;\">被確診為2019新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCoV）肺炎患者。</span><br />\n<br />\n日前Red Velvet準備23日日本大阪場巡迴演出，<span style=\"color: red;\">22日抵達金浦機場出境時沒有任何防備措施和載上口罩，24日回國時抵達金浦機場也沒有準備任何防護措施</span>，多名粉絲發現Red Velvet成員Irene不斷咳嗽，疑似受感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/aopl/202001240039.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202001240039.aspx&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX2WzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=3cfd9dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/aopl/202001240039.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"0a342007ed13a39e748b5034f8539de80aea8950","tid":1838804,"uid":317979,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21bbd945ba12ab173db9ad9968096eb3ff56a93","tid":1838804,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"唔好有事